cs per se than about the inescapable ambivalence of all human feeling.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCarnivalzSpainzAndalusia. 0aSex rolezSpainzAndalusia. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Customs & Traditions.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000z978311053801440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030014394240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300143942423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300143942/original  a978-3-11-053801-4  Yale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles